{"tid":1144460,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【星戰迷點睇】迪士尼宣佈再拍全新《星球大戰》三部曲","createTime":"2019-05-08T05:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T06:34:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"b22c657cbe8f82a210c4228ee632afe7653575cf","tid":1144460,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"《星球大戰》系列（Star Wars）陪伴幾代人成長，由荷李活名導J.J. Abrams執導的新三部曲，將於今年底第三集《Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker》上映後告一段落，雖然新作毀譽參半，仍無阻其在全球開出亮眼票房，前兩集目前仍穩坐史上最高票房第四及第十二位。<br />\n有見《星戰》多年來依然有驚人號召力，迪士尼今日宣佈再拍全新三部曲，幕後班底包括《星球大戰：最後絕地武士》（Star Wars: The Last Jedi）編劇Rian Johnson、《權力遊戲》（Game of Thrones）主創David Benioff和D.B. Weiss，預計分別於2022、2024和2026年上映，繼續攻佔聖誕檔期。迪士尼目前未透露任何其他細節，不過消息一傳出已引起網民反彈，不少粉絲認為再拍續集只會打爛《星戰》的招牌，紛紛勸迪士尼收手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557286857_aa1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557286857_aa1b.jpg&h=f0b02867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJ.J. Abrams執導的新三部曲評價兩極。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190508/59576315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F59576315&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=008524a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F59576315&h=aa5453be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190508/59576315</a>"},{"pid":"308bc326305f5442e3c29a456d397edf9054a387","tid":1144460,"uid":2785,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"出下外傳咪算囉 搞咁多野做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21d98897fd8982e93fffb3afa5b48f2672adb12","tid":1144460,"uid":23635,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0